---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 321
  - Title: Hermenia of Athos
    Number: 445
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Symbolism=The Worship of Images
---
All honor that we pay the image, we refer to the Archetype, namely Him
whose image it is. ... In no wise honor we the colors or the art, but
the archetype in Christ, who is in heaven.
